Package: secubox-routes
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), iproute2
Description: SecuBox Routes - Routing table viewer and manager
 SecuBox module for viewing and managing routing tables,
 policy routing rules, and ARP/NDP neighbors.
 .
 Features:
  - View IPv4 and IPv6 routes
  - Add/delete routes dynamically
  - Policy routing rules management
  - ARP/NDP neighbor table viewer
  - Route cache flush capability
 .
 Part of the SecuBox security appliance suite.
